# Loyalty API

Back end for the White Label Loyalty mobile App
## Business [/bussiness]
### Create Bussiness [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "name": "business name",
            "branches": 2
            "tills": 3
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /questions/2

    + Body

            {
                "id": 1
            }
## Products [/product]
### Create Products [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "products": [
                {
                    "plu": "23232ewe",
                    "branch_id": 2
                    "desc": "Small Coffee"
                }
            ]
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /questions/2

    + Body

            {
                "products": [
                    {
                        "id": 1,
                        "plu": "23232ewe",
                        "branch_id": 2
                        "desc": "Small Coffee"
                    }
                ]
            }


